      "content": "thanks for the detail. i'm asking because i have some clients who have very different hair textures and cultural styles. specifically, how should someone with very curly or textured/kinky hair approach this? for example, if they want to look \"serious\" and \"unobtrusive\" like you mentioned, should they be looking into smoothing it out or using certain products to keep it sleek? i want to make sure they fit that \"polished\" look you're describing for leadership.",
